summary:
I've worked in Sales and Marketing for over 8 years in various management positions. I have 8 years of Face to Face marketing experience, 7 years of management experience, and 3 years of experience as an English Teacher. 

Nowadays, my focus is sharing knowledge, I use various didactic models to train others, either in sales, management or speaking English. Working both as a consultant and English teacher

Honorary titles obtained
-Ambassador of the year for the Dutch Red Cross in 2017
-Ambassador of the year for SOS children's villages in 2018
-Ambassador of the year for Amnesty International in 2020
